<BR>
As far as I can make out, you have to ESCape from the game, select which
type of bat you want, then go back into the game. Obviously, you can't
have more than one type of bat.<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <i>(Gerard Sweeney in Hack Attack III)</i> 
<br>
</td></tr>
